name: 李老师不是你老师
content: January 31, Yuncheng, Shanxi. A circus lion suddenly bit a tourist leaning against the cage during a performance. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1885358495282978816/pu/img/L5wsKhIsPwimKv7E.jpg

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On January 28, a man accused Jiangsu Satellite TV of malicious editing. The man said that Jiangsu Satellite TV interviewed him, "When relatives asked him some offensive questions, how would you answer?" The man said that his answer at the time was "Maybe others will say that my affairs have nothing to do with you, but I won't say that. I will communicate with my elders in a friendly manner." As a result, Jiangsu Satellite TV edited out "My affairs have nothing to do with you" and misinterpreted the man's original intention. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1885363638120439808/pu/img/N3CClKHaF9RCrX47.jpg

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: It is said online that a citizen called the duty room of Jiangxi Provincial Government and angrily denounced the local government for not taking action, saying that it was fascist Japan. The public still does not know whether Li Yixue is dead or alive. The man said that he would organize the people of the country to overthrow the provincial government, launch another Nanchang Uprising, and blow up the door of the provincial government. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1885369253710495744/pu/img/ID9QPLjOjQ-5qRXh.jpg

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: January 31 (Release) A retired soldier called the Ministry of Foreign Affairs Personnel Service Bureau and said that he saw news a few days ago that the import of Japanese aquatic products would be resumed. He accused the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of losing party spirit and principles, having no national consciousness, and being unqualified to represent the people. He also accused the government of importing foreign genetically modified agricultural and sideline products on the phone. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1885390466226827264/pu/img/yzoM2MqK9gFcUFap.jpg

content:
In the early morning of February 1, Tencent QQ Small World was suspected of having a serious censorship loophole, and a large amount of June 4th, insults to parents and pornographic content suddenly appeared. 
So far, most of these contents have been cleared. https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Gip7ermX0AAF2YN.jpg

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On January 31, US Secretary of State Rubio said in an interview with Megyn Kelly that he did not hear Chinese Foreign Minister Wang Yi warn him to "be careful" during a call. 
"But they like to play this trick, saying one thing in English and another in Chinese, but at least I didn't hear it, otherwise I would say the same thing... But it's boring and irrelevant. What really matters is our future decisions" https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1885493828167081984/pu/img/dl5ycOqHqqUQz1P4.jpg
